CK-Lister
------------------------------------------------------------------
Directory Lister is a simple PHP based script created to let you list the
contents of a directory and all sub directories and allow you to navigate
there within.  Just download and install Directory Lister to any web
directory and have immediate access to all files and sub-direcories under
that directory.


Installation
------------------------------------------------------------------
To install CK-Lister, simply upload index.php and the ck-lister folder to
the directory that you would like to have listed.


